{"tid":1526012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"901 機場攻略 麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:28:21.000Z","uid":108910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2865a4874d5f3bbbb41583c45c635d06637e3961","tid":1526012,"uid":108910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:56:30.000Z","msg":"- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2Xwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=d48b0fb3\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5ba8cf0ea313f6ea5d8d53fe70a2c4e7b135c3b","tid":1526012,"uid":100046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0ETUfk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0ETUfk.jpg&h=de775021&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63e79748d03b